string.name: sourceUrlOrGameIds
string.comment:
sourceUrlOrGameIds
In the "New live broadcast" form, a field for specifying the game(s). Description:
URL that Lichess will check to get PGN updates. It must be publicly accessible from the Internet. Alternatively, you can enter up to 64 Lichess game IDs, separated by spaces.

resources.string: URL-leinki, ið Lichess fer at kanna til tess at fáa PGN dagføringar. Leinkið nýtist at vera alment atkomiligt á alnetinum.
Til ber eisini ístaðin at skriva 64 Lichess-samleikar upp. Teir noyðast at vera skildir sundur við millumrúmum.
Valfrítt, um tú veitst, nær tiltakið byrjar
